1
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,480
You...

2
00:01:20,160 --> 00:01:21,120
You...

3
00:01:21,320 --> 00:01:22,440
are rebelling!

4
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:25,080
Guards, throw them all out!

5
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:46,020
I've wanted to hit you for a long time.

6
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,000
Master Du,

7
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:51,580
why is this necessary?

8
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:54,520
We just want to do our part for the townspeople.

9
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,759
That sounds nice.

10
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,160
Do your part?

11
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,920
You are clearly challenging my authority.

12
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,780
Let me tell you,

13
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:06,160
as long as I, Du Zong, am still alive,

14
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,680
they

15
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,539
will never get a drop of medicine.

16
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,720
Don't dirty your hands.

17
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:12,440
Duzong,

18
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,200
you are too stubborn.

19
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,560
In that case,

20
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:16,860
we will take our leave.

21
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,640
Let's go.

22
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,960
Father, I want to go with them.

23
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:24,920
You unfilial son!

24
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:25,920
What did you say?

25
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:30,960
I said,

26
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,560
I want to go with them.

27
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:33,600
I can't just stand by

28
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,930
and watch you make mistake after mistake.

29
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,440
You...

30
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,760
A son of a concubine

31
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,490
will never amount to anything.

32
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,160
If your legitimate brother were still here,

33
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:44,090
I wouldn't even spare you a glance.

34
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,920
I'd like to lend you two a hand.

35
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,360
Okay.

36
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,820
Let's go together.

37
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:55,960
Good.

38
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,880
Just you wait.

39
00:02:57,880 --> 00:02:59,740
I won't let you get away with this.

40
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:17,530
You sent Duyu back to the house to treat the patients.

41
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,520
Where are you going?

42
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:22,760
I'm thinking about the herb supply.

43
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:25,640
Although I can go up the mountain to gather herbs now,

44
00:03:25,640 --> 00:03:28,040
there are too many patients in the alley.

45
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,480
The herbs gathered for now

46
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:31,280
are far from enough.

47
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,400
Don't worry too much.

48
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,360
We'll cross that bridge when we come to it.

49
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,760
Let's gather some herbs as a reserve first.

50
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:38,640
Okay.

51
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,960
I saw you liked candied hawthorn the other day.

52
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,290
They happen to be selling some over there.

53
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,760
Thank you.

54
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,290
Are you feeling any better?

55
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,080
Our tastes are quite similar.

56
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:17,410
I've loved eating this since I was a child.

57
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,720
Actually,

58
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:23,280
I don't like sweets.

59
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:24,770
It's just...

60
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,400
It's just...

61
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,250
because of that Jiujiu?

62
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,120
Oh.

63
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,200
Do you take me for a swill bucket?

64
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:59,220
What's given to me is mine.

65
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,860
There's no taking it back.

66
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,760
Let's go.

67
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,200
That is rosemary.

68
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,080
This is Snow of June.

69
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,360
Right?

70
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,159
Yes.

71
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,860
I feel like I've been here before.

72
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,400
Xiao Heyan.

73
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:49,400
I'm afraid Duzong will cause trouble for Duyu and Chuyun.

74
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:50,960
I'm worried.

75
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,159
Why don't you go back and check?

76
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:54,020
What about you?

77
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,980
I still need to pick another herb.

78
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,530
I'll go with you.

79
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,000
It's not safe for you to be alone.

80
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,320
I know a lot of herbs now.

81
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,120
I can help you.

82
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:07,160
Look, this is rosemary.

83
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,760
This one.

84
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,040
June Snow.

85
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:12,960
Right?

86
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,880
What's wrong?

87
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,200
Nothing.

88
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,760
Let's finish picking herbs

89
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,960
and go back early.

90
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,780
What are you doing?

91
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,800
He started it.

92
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,400
You were sent by the Du Sect.

93
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,400
Humph.

94
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,760
You're quite smart, little girl.

95
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,720
You two outsiders

96
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:11,730
dare to cause trouble in Sitai Town

97
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,920
without asking about Master Du's methods.

98
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,000
Duzong, as the head of the medical hall,

99
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,120
is such a bully.

100
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,400
He has no medical ethics.

101
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,860
Is there any justice left?

102
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,530
Justice?

103
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,640
Here,

104
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,600
I am the law.

105
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:27,560
I must teach you a lesson today.

106
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,600
Get them!

107
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,080
Who is blind enough to offend me?

108
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,960
Oh, my.

109
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,280
Lord Zhou, you're here to buy herbs?

110
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:02,980
These two broke the rules.

111
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:05,450
I was just about to teach them a lesson.

112
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:13,880
Miss Ji,

113
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,320
why are you here?

114
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,800
No need for formalities.

115
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:20,120
Lord Zhou.

116
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,520
How dare you treat two outsiders

117
00:08:21,520 --> 00:08:22,160
so rudely?

118
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,680
Are you blind?

119
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,760
How dare you bully

120
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:29,400
my saviors?

121
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,480
Guards!

122
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,600
Take him back and teach him a lesson.

123
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,600
It's a misunderstanding!

124
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,480
It's a misunderstanding, My Lord!

125
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,320
It's a misunderstanding!

126
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,480
Lord Zhou.

127
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,320
Thank you, then.

128
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,080
Ah, Miss Ji.

129
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,440
Where are you going?

130
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,700
Allow me to escort you.

131
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:52,360
Lord Zhou, we're not close.

132
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,440
Please behave yourself.

133
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,200
Miss Ji,

134
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,760
last time you treated me with acupuncture

135
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,960
and saved my life.

136
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,960
I can't thank you enough,

137
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:01,000
so I wouldn't dare have other thoughts.

138
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,480
It's just that there might have been a misunderstanding last time.

139
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:06,120
I didn't know you were a miracle doctor.

140
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,200
I spoke out of turn.

141
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,160
If I caused any offense,

142
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,640
please forgive me, Miss.

143
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,920
What do you want?

144
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:18,600
Miss Ji saved my life,

145
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,840
so I wish to repay her kindness.

146
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:24,120
Besides, I was hoping that in the future,

147
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:27,520
Miss Ji might put in a good word for me with the Prime Minister.

148
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:31,960
I'm afraid that is your true motive.

149
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,480
People like you only care about getting promoted and getting rich.

150
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,960
Have you ever considered the hardships of commoners seeking medical help?

151
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,480
Ouch.

152
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,200
Miss Ji, you are mistaken.

153
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:41,760
As one of the dynasty's only two Imperial Merchants,

154
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:42,400
I am specifically in charge of

155
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,520
the Imperial Hospital's affairs,

156
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,880
recruiting famous doctors nationwide,

157
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,600
and purchasing medicinal herbs.

158
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,120
His Majesty specifically instructed me

159
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,960
to pay attention to the people's suffering

160
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,840
and report it promptly.

161
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:00,760
Are you two going up the mountain to pick herbs?

162
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:02,400
Oh, why go to such trouble?

163
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,560
Follow me.

164
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:04,520
Come.

165
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:05,360
Please.

166
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:14,520
Master.

167
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,500
We brought the Young Master back.

168
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,720
You scoundrel.

169
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:24,010
You actually humiliated your father in public for an outsider.

170
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:27,160
Master Du.

171
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,840
Master Du.

172
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,160
From today on,

173
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,560
this clinic

174
00:10:37,760 --> 00:10:39,560
belongs to me.

175
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,000
Lord Zhou,

176
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,280
this clinic is my life's work.

177
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,560
I cannot comply.

178
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,360
What?

179
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:46,680
You refuse?

180
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:49,000
Then I will report to the Imperial Court immediately,

181
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:53,080
detailing your high fees and refusal to dispense medicine.

182
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:56,280
Let's see if you can keep this clinic open.

183
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:58,920
There is no need to force him.

184
00:10:58,920 --> 00:11:01,160
As long as he promises to treat patients

185
00:11:01,760 --> 00:11:03,400
regardless of status.

186
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:06,400
He is afraid of this Lord Zhou now.

187
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,210
As soon as he leaves,

188
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,120
this old man will turn on us.

189
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,080
Shen Yi, what do you mean?

190
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,800
Are you questioning my integrity?

191
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:18,580
Does your integrity even need questioning?

192
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,040
You have a point.

193
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:21,520
However,

194
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:24,660
even though Duzong isn't fit to practice medicine,

195
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:27,600
this medical hall is his property.

196
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,520
If we take it by force...

197
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,320
That is a bit too cruel.

198
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,240
Indeed.

199
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,200
This medical hall is my lifeblood.

200
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,480
If you take it by force,

201
00:11:37,680 --> 00:11:38,480
I...

202
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,280
I will end my life.

203
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,540
Master, please don't!

204
00:11:43,960 --> 00:11:44,800
Lord Zhou,

205
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,600
Doctor Ji,

206
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:48,450
How about letting me manage the medical hall?

207
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,280
If I manage it,

208
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,480
as a member of the Du family,

209
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:59,760
it wouldn't be considered taking it by force.

210
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:02,220
I will also benefit the people of Sitai Town,

211
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:04,360
so everyone can buy medicine.

212
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:11,320
Very well.

213
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:15,520
Duyu, you unfilial son!

214
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,080
How dare you!

215
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:16,760
Duzong.

216
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:19,780
Since your son wants to run the business,

217
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:23,560
stop making a scene.

218
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,240
I...

219
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,120
Doctor Ji!

220
00:12:25,360 --> 00:12:27,280
Bad news! Someone is dying!

221
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:01,400
Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

222
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:01,400
Yi, Yi, Nan.

223
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,280
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng.

224
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,000
Xiao, Xiao, Xue, Yi, Yi, Nan.

225
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,600
Xiao, Xiao, Xue, Yi, Yi, Nan.

226
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,800
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

227
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:35,960
Pan, Xiu, Long.

228
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:35,840
Lyu, Sun, Zhang.

229
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,160
Pan, Xiang, Long.

230
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:36,720
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

231
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:36,400
Xiu, Long.

232
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:36,720
Pan, Xiu, Chong.
